name: 6 Songs: From Me, To U.
description:
6 songs. 6 memories. 6 epiphanies. 
6 tears. 6 skipped heartbeats. 

1. Overture/Aslan's Song
2. Here We Go. One By One.
3. Robots Can Spell
4. My Weary Heart
5. Melancholy Monday
6. Farewell, Until We Meet Again

All songs are created entirely by Chatawinna. (Select songs can be heard @ http://www.myspace.com/chatawinna)
